  "title": "Project Manager (LTA Project)",
  "description": "<h2><u>Project Manager (LTA Project)</u></h2>\n<p>Responsibility:<br>\nLead a team of Supervisors to manage day to day construction activities<br>\nCoordinate with the Client, QP(S) and QP(D) to resolve technical and design problems<br>\nHandle sub-contractors and specialists to ensure work is completed according to specifications and schedule<br>\n<br>\nRequirement:<br>\nPossess Bachelors Degree in Civil Engineering recognised by BCA<br>\nWith minimum 3years experience in construction preferably in LTA projects<br>\nFamiliar with LTA station works and/or tunnel works<br>\nFamiliar with Singapore and International construction specifications and standards<br>\nFamiliar with preparation of construction method statements and Risk Assessments</p>",
